title: Who's A Better Astrological Match For These Celebrity Men?
description:
A while back Kristin earned the right to pick a random bit for us to do without warning – we called it “Kristin's Stupid Bit of The Week.”. And today she has an interested game for us to play. 
Who's the better astrological match for these celebrity cheaters? Their partner or mistress?
